{
  "stem": "1132.3",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So that's another very, very vivid memory that I do have.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I have recollections of school having started.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And I have-- in that context, I went to school and finished first grade in six weeks.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "But we were declared having finished first grade, and we were promoted to go to second grade.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Everybody just simply wanted to go on with their lives.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "I remember everybody was looking for their friends, who survived and who was there, whether it was Jew or Christian.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "That, that is something that I remember.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "I remembered the city, which is a gorgeous city, being in total ruins.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "There are-- the city used to be called Little Paris because it has the two sides of the river dividing it and the bridges connecting them.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And the bridges were all destroyed.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "So I have recollection of this pontoon bridge that was first created so that people could cross the river from either side and how slowly the city was-- began to come back.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "I also remember how my father was trying to reestablish his law practice.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "Now, we didn't talk much about the fact how he was not allowed to practice and how all the Jews had to be reinstated as life came back by the Bar Association to be allowed to practice again.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And so he was among those who got himself early reinstated.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "I remember the political turmoil, to some extent.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "There were a lot of political parties.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] There were-- the communists were very slow in asserting themselves.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "I remember my sister, who has become a young woman who was dating.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "I have memories of her dating.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I have memories of, of parties, her parties, as life was trying to return to normal in my house.",
      "word_count": 23
    }
  ],
